{"tid":2127583,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"一年前嘅今日 727元朗嘅事 你地忘記左？","createTime":"2020-07-27T11:46:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-27T23:39:35.000Z","uid":347812,"like":92,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":73,"replies":[{"pid":"f2c05bcd9deb23ef26dc2e1cdcb88c538aa4fa00","tid":2127583,"uid":347812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T11:46:38.000Z","msg":"上年7月27號<br />\n係光復元朗遊行既一日<br />\n面對721元朗白衣暴徒恐襲<br />\n我地決定保護家園<br />\n但當日則比警方<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"large\">首次發出反對通知書</span></span><br />\n最後香港人冇理 繼續企出嚟<br />\n而當日光復元朗遊行係有<span class=\"red\">288000人參與</span><br />\n到夜晚 大家着住gear留守元朗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但結果就係有防暴速龍衝上元朗黨鐵站打市民<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日係一週年 我希望所有人都記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q0SYGhs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq0SYGhs.jpg&h=d4b3c98f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/042YGht.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F042YGht.jpg&h=718e9ce0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MWxt3vP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMWxt3vP.jpg&h=eee2a482&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9bVWsXX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9bVWsXX.jpg&h=ee6562f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9U8w1hY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9U8w1hY.jpg&h=ab44ae93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c3d1D4D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc3d1D4D.jpg&h=945aa673&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S85SLKE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS85SLKE.jpg&h=87442890&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br 